        <h3>Article VII. Meetings </h3>
        <p>Meetings shall be held every week during the Friday common hour. Members will be notified prior to any change in the meeting time or location.</p>
        <h3>Article VIII. Conduct</h3>
        <ul>
            <li>Section 1. This chapter and its members agree to uphold and abide by the rules and regulations of New Jersey Institute of Technology.</li>
